name: Unstable Babies
description:
I'm trying to recreate some of the art from board game "Unstable Unicorns", starting with the babies, but it seems kinda hard to get some variations that fit with the game artstyle.

It is my first try, so any feedback is helpful.

It works better with square images, it also works fine with many styles (last images) besides the "base" style.

A bit overcooked maybe, it works better around: 0.7 ~ 0.9

You totally need: "unicorn, cartoon, baby unicorn" in your prompt to keep the base style, you can remove it to make something with another style.

Optional: "horn, wings, hickey"

modelVersions.name: v0.5
modelVersions.description: First version, kinda unstable, hard to get some gens that fit with the game artstyle. Pretty good with many styles.
